INSERT INTO `brinth_diamonds` VALUES 
(1,'diamonds2','The Broken Vase','diamonds2.png','This happened at 3:15 am. Only 3 people were in the castle.','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes: <br><br> I was in the kitchen making tea.. Didn\'t hear of anything strange\", \"Walter: <br><br> I passed from the Library before 03:15 am to grab a book.\", \"Jane: <br><br>I was reading in the living room and heard of something strange at 03:10\"]','{\"Who did it?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"When did it happen?\": [\"03:00 am\", \"03:10 am\", \"03:15 am\"]}','{\"Who did it?\": \"Walter\", \"When did it happen?\": \"03:10 am\"}','Walter did it at 3:10 AM<br>Anton saw him'),
(2,'diamonds3','The Locked Drawer','diamonds3.png','A drawer in the victim\'s desk was found broken into. An object is missing.<br>Time of incident: 9:30 PM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes: <br><br> I was preparing papers in the living room. I haven\'t been near the office all night.\", \"Walter: <br><br>I was in the basement reading. I didn\'t get out of there until 01:00.\", \"Jane: <br><br>I stopped by the office a little after midnight. I wanted to leave a note to the victim.\"]','{\"What is missing?\": [\"The Drawer\'s key\", \"The Pen\", \"A Pendant\"], \"Who broken into?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"]}','{\"What is missing?\": \"A Pendant\", \"Who broken into?\": \"Jane\"}','According to the Camera, Jane was there last night.<br>\nShe took the Pendant - revealing she\'s Alistair\'s Daughter'),
(3,'diamonds4','The Fake Alibi','diamonds4.png','One of the guests lied about where they were at the time of the disappearance.','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes: <br><br> I was in the lounge reading ‘The Last Page’. I was just relaxing.\", \"Walter: <br><br>I was outside in the garden smoking. I didn’t even go near the lounge.\", \"Jane: <br><br>I was making tea in the kitchen. I didn’t pay attention to what was happening around me.\"]','{\"Who lied?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"Which clue proves it?\": [\"The Camera\", \"The fingertips on the book\", \"The dusty Shelf\"]}','{\"Who lied?\": \"Agnes\", \"Which clue proves it?\": \"The Camera\"}',NULL),
(4,'diamonds5','The Shadow in the Window','diamonds5.png','Someone was observing the victim’s room from the window<br>Time of incident: 9:15 PM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_anton.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I was in my room, sleeping since 01:30 AM.\", \"Walter:<br><br>I was in the kitchen around that time. Didn’t step outside or near the east wing, if that’s what you\'re asking.\", \"Jane:<br><br>I was in the bathroom at the time. I didn’t even know anything happened.\", \"Anton:<br><br>I was doing my last round near the east garden. I saw movement by the window, but I didn’t want to interrupt. I just kept walking.\"]','{\"Who Was outside the window?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\", \"Anton\"]}','{\"Who Was outside the window?\": \"Anton\"}','Anton was outside the window observing the conversation between Alistair and another person.'),
(5,'diamonds6','The Missing Letter','diamonds6.png','An important letter disappeared before it was read.<br>Time of incident: 10:00 PM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I saw the fireplace smoking, but I didn’t notice who was nearby.\", \"Walter:<br><br>I have no idea about any letter. I was in the garden nearly all the afternoon.\", \"Jane:<br><br>I just wanted to warm up a little. The weather was frosty.\"]','{\"Whose fault is this?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"What happened to the letter?\": [\"Missing\", \"Stolen\", \"Burnt\"]}','{\"Whose fault is this?\": \"Jane\", \"What happened to the letter?\": \"Burnt\"}','Jane got rid of it by burning it in the fireplace.<br>The letter was naming Jane as heir.'),
(6,'diamonds7','The Poisoned Tea','diamonds7.png','The victim drank his tea and collapsed.<br>Time of incident: 9:45 PM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I didn’t touch anything, I was waiting for the victim to come and we were just talking.\", \"Walter:<br><br>I was nearby but never approached the tray. I didn’t even go near the cups.\", \"Jane:<br><br>I brought the tea, but I left 5 minutes later to help Anton in the pantry.\"]','{\"Whose fault is this?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"Which cup was poisoned?\": [\"Cup 1\", \"Cup 2\", \"Cup 3\", \"Cup 4\"]}','{\"Whose fault is this?\": \"Walter\", \"Which cup was poisoned?\": \"Cup 2\"}','Walter slipped poison into the second cup of tea while Jane was away.'),
(7,'diamonds8','The Hidden Back Room','diamonds8.png','Someone entered the basement through a secret passage.','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes: <br><br>I never went to the basement. I\'m afraid of dark places, and I don\'t even know where the candles are.\", \"Walter: <br><br>I passed by the library for a while, but I didn\'t touch anything. I was just looking for a magazine.\", \"Jane: <br><br>I didn\'t go that way. I was in the kitchen doing the dishes.\"]','{\"Which clue proves that?\": [\"Unlocked Door\", \"The melted candle\", \"Scratches in the bookcase\"], \"Who went to the hidden room?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"]}','{\"Which clue proves that?\": \"The melted candle\", \"Who went to the hidden room?\": \"Walter\"}','Walter used the secret passage and the candle proves it.'),
(8,'diamonds9','The Defaced Portrait','diamonds9.png','Victim\'s portrait was found torn and painted red. <br> Free clue by Devs: The frame was torn from left to right.','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes: <br><br>I didn\'t even go into the art gallery.\", \"Walter: <br><br>I wasn’t even interested in the painting. I paint landscapes, not faces.\", \"Jane: <br><br>Okay, We had a little fight.. But I would never destroy art.\"]','{\"Who did it?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"What was the motive?\": [\"Bad Blood\", \"Artistic reaction\", \"Accident\"]}','{\"Who did it?\": \"Jane\", \"What was the motive?\": \"Bad Blood\"}','Jane destroyed the victim\'s art because of rancor.'),
(9,'diamonds10','Attempted Murder','diamonds10.png','Victim\'s car had been sabotaged<br>Walter was supposed to take the car, he mentioned it earlier to two guests<br>Jane took the car by accident a few minutes earlier.<br>Time of incident: 1:30 AM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I didn’t know Jane would take it... I just thought something was off about Walter.\", \"Walter:<br><br>Yes, I had arranged the car for the morning. Didn’t expect anyone else to use it.\", \"Jane:<br><br>I don’t know anything about brakes or cars. I just borrowed it for a quick errand.\"]','{\"Who did it?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"Who was the target\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Jane\"], \"How would that happen?\": [\"Poison\", \"Cut brakes\", \"Explosive device\"]}','{\"Who did it?\": \"Agnes\", \"Who was the target\": \"Walter\", \"How would that happen?\": \"Cut brakes\"}','Agnes sabotaged the car because she has been suspicious of Walter for some time, but Jane accidentally took it instead.'),
(10,'diamonds11','The Vanished Servant','diamonds11.png','Anton the butler goes missing.<br>His uniform is later found floating in the lake.<br>Time of disappearance: Around 3:00 AM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I saw someone walking quickly past the warehouse, but I couldn’t figure out who it was.\", \"Walter:<br><br>Anton had told me in the past that he was thinking about leaving, but I didn’t believe him.\", \"Jane:<br><br>Was the suit in the lake? Someone probably threw it there… or did he want us to think something else?\"]','{\"What do you think happened? He...\": [\"Got murdered\", \"is hiding on the Castle\", \"Escaped\"]}','{\"What do you think happened? He...\": \"Escaped\"}','Anton escaped and left misleading traces behind — including his uniform in the lake and a cryptic message to hide his trail.'),
(11,'diamonds12','Fake ID','diamonds12.png','A new visitor arrives at the estate claiming to recognize Walter... but not as Walter.<br>Agnes makes a public accusation. Jane is caught in the middle.<br>Time of confrontation: 6:30 AM','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_stranger.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I’ve been saying it for days. That man is not who he says he is. His story doesn’t match up. I found an old photo... and he’s not in it.\", \"Walter:<br><br>This is absurd. I’ve lived a quiet life. Of course I changed jobs, of course I moved around. That proves nothing.\", \"Jane:<br><br>I don’t know what’s happening... but Agnes seems really convinced. And that stranger knew him by another name.\", \"Stranger:<br><br>I worked with him five years ago in Bellmire. His name was Ledger. Walter Brinth died overseas... I attended the funeral.\"]','{\"Who is lying?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Walter\", \"Stranger\"], \"What is Walter\'s real name?\": [\"Walter\", \"Ledger\", \"Unknown\"]}','{\"Who is lying?\": \"Walter\", \"What is Walter\'s real name?\": \"Ledger\"}','Walter is actually Ledger, an impostor who assumed Walter Brinth’s identity years ago. The stranger’s testimony and Agnes’s digging confirm the truth.'),
(12,'diamonds13','Reveal the Killer','diamonds13.png','All evidence has been gathered. The final question remains:<br><br>Who killed Lord Alistair Brinth?<br><br>Time of murder: 3:10 AM – but the plan began long before that.','[\"brinth_diamonds_agnes.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_jane.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_stranger.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_evelyne.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_anton.png\", \"brinth_diamonds_walter.png\"]','[\"Agnes:<br><br>I knew something was wrong since the second day. The forged signature, the passport, the way he avoided questions. Ledger has a reason to fake his identity.\", \"Jane:<br><br>Well, He never even knew Alistair’s dog’s name. How could he be his brother? But still... murder?\", \"Stranger:<br><br>I heard him years ago knowing his father had something to do with Alistair and he looked suspicious. That is why I came\", \"Lady Evelyne:<br><br>Alistair had enemies. He always did. But I never thought they’d walk in wearing his brother’s shoes.\", \"Anton:<br><br>**Came back, is alive and fine and is here to confess**<br><br>I saw Ledger leaving the archives that night. He didn’t notice me. I followed. He is the murderer.\", \"Ledger:<br><br>Me? This is insane. You’re taking the word of a gardener and a woman who paints ghosts. Get a grip.\"]','{\"What was the motive?\": [\"Revenge\", \"Greed\", \"Fear of being exposed\"], \"Who killed Alistair?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Jane\", \"Ledger\", \"Anton\"], \"What exposed the killer?\": [\"Passport\", \"Letter\", \"Tea Cup\", \"Mirror Message\"], \"How was the murder committed?\": [\"Poisoned Tea\", \"Pushed Down the Stairs\", \"Car Trap\"], \"Who first discovered the truth?\": [\"Agnes\", \"Jane\", \"Anton\", \"Stranger\"]}','{\"What was the motive?\": \"Revenge\", \"Who killed Alistair?\": \"Ledger\", \"What exposed the killer?\": \"Passport\", \"How was the murder committed?\": \"Pushed Down the Stairs\", \"Who first discovered the truth?\": \"Anton\"}','Ledger was the murderer. These were his final words:<br><br><img src=\"../../brinth_icons/diamonds/result.png\" class=\"main-image\">');
